### 8. Create a new Venue (as Admin)
# @name createVenue
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/venues
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}

{
  "name": "Main Campus Auditorium",
  "latitude": -6.7766,
  "longitude": 39.2312,
  "radius": 100
}

> {%
    client.global.set("venueId", response.body.id);
