### 9. Attempt to create a Venue (as Attendee) - EXPECT 403 FORBIDDEN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/venues
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{attendee_jwt}}

{
  "name": "Should Not Be Created",
  "latitude": 0,
  "longitude": 0,
  "radius": 10
}


### 10. Get all Venues (as Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/venues
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}


### 11. Get a single Venue by ID (as Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/venues/{{venueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}


### 12. Update an existing Venue (as Admin)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/venues/{{venueId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}

{
  "name": "Main Campus Auditorium (Updated)",
  "latitude": -6.7767,
  "longitude": 39.2313,
  "radius": 110
}


### 13. Delete the Venue (as Admin)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/venues/{{venueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}
